name: Comirnaty - Water for injections
description:
A generative, glitch and sono poem cooked by mixing Comirnaty excipients only.

Grab a dose at the price of a real Comirnaty dose for the European market (we recommend at least two doses!).

A collaboration between hex6c (generative), Domenico Barra (glitch), and Ilaria Boffa (voice and sound manipulation).

Read the full story on Medium (bit.ly/comirnaty)
